Speaker 1: How can I help you today, Jeff?

Speaker 2: Yeah, could you do that?

Speaker 1: Yeah, of course.

Speaker 1: We're always here.

Speaker 2: Monday through Friday.

Speaker 1: All right, gotcha.

Speaker 2: Thank you, all right, thank you so much.

Speaker 1: You have a nice rest of your shift.

Speaker 2: Yeah, you too, bye.
